<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8">
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
  <style>
    body {
      margin: 0;
      padding: 0;
      box-sizing: border-box;
      font-family: 'Poppins', sans-serif;
      background-color: #F5F5F5;
      color: black;
      background-image: url(../img/noise-bg.png);
    }

    .container {
      max-width: 1200px;
      margin: 0 auto;
      padding: 20px;
    }

    .div {
      display: flex;
      flex-direction: column;
      justify-content: center;
      align-items: center;
      padding: 50px 20px;
    }

    .div-2 {
      border-radius: 25px;
      box-shadow: 1px 4px 14.7px 0px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.25);
      background-color: #fff;
      display: flex;
      flex-direction: column;
      gap: 20px;
      margin: 48px 0 45px;
      padding: 68px;
    }

    .div-3 {
      align-self: center;
      display: flex;
      flex-grow: 1;
      flex-basis: 0%;
      flex-direction: column;
      align-items: center;
      margin: auto 0;
    }

    .div-4 {
      color: #000;
      text-align: center;
      font: 400 56px Londrina Solid, sans-serif;
    }

    .div-5 {
      color: #000;
      text-align: center;
      margin-top: 15px;
      font: 400 25px Iowan Old Style, sans-serif;
    }

    .div-6 {
      color: #000;
      text-align: center;
      margin-top: 20px;
      font: 400 16px Iowan Old Style, sans-serif;
    }

    .login-button {
      background-color: #cddbcd;
      color: black;
      cursor: pointer;
      transition: background-color 0.3s ease;
      text-align: center;
      border-radius: 93px;
      align-self: center;
      justify-content: center;
      margin: 20px 0;
      padding: 15px;
      font: 700 20px Sometype Mono, sans-serif;
      border: none;
      outline: none;
    }
  </style>
</head>

<body>
  <div class="container">
    <div class="div">
      <div class="div-2">
        <div class="div-3">
          <div class="div-4">The NoteBook</div>
          <div class="div-5">Your ultimate study tool</div>
          <div class="div-6">
            With the NoteBook, take notes without distractions,
            <br />
            while having access to them anywhere online.
            <br />
            <a href="/auth/google" class="btn btn-primary btn-lg"><button class="login-button">LOGIN</button></a>
            <br />
            Powered by AI, the NoteBook summarizes your notes in seconds,
            making it easier for you to focus on what is really important.
            <br />
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</body>
</html>